cdata.name: Pebbles
cdata.desc:
Publica is a decentralized publishing platform that plans to connect authors and readers. The publica platform will leverage the Ethereum blockchain to create the largest publisher, in which readers can purchase (with BOOK tokens) access keys for the literary. The content will be stored in a decentralized immutable storage allowing the publisher to have zero inventory and at the same time provide an platform with a variety of literary accessible. 

Publica's PBL Tokens known as Pebbles are ERC20 compliant assets in the ethereum network-.
